Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日出登山？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是为了看日出 晚上登富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一片漆黑中 灯排成光的队列
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.24,0:01:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之中专心致志的登山
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.29,0:01:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是在我还是高中生的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.29,0:01:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是和朋友一起第一次登山
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.92,0:01:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是一无所知 非常紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面是一片云彩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面是漫天的星空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和平时居住的地方简直就像是两个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.23,0:02:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢 然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:15.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我一起去的朋友半路累瘫了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:19.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别…别管我 你先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像电视剧一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他虽然很有体力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却没有把握好节奏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就一个人登上了山顶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:37.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和很多人一起在山顶看天空变亮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家看着同一个方向
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界被渲染成红色 非常漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我一生都无法忘记的回忆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:58.40,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(538,420)}为了做喜欢做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说日向
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从以前就开始在想了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要去登富士山？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK 富士山挺好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久之前还那么不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到会变成自己说想去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 不要说那个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就趁热打铁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就去看登富士山需要的道具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和三增峠一样的装备不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是晚上登 需要头灯的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又没有路灯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:52.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手电筒不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手里都塞满了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 就算是夏天也很冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:04:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好穿成严冬的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,严冬？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:04.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请教教我吧 枫老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山上的气温标高每升高100米 就会下降0.6°
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,标高3776米的话 比地上约低22°
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:22.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算地上是30° 富士山顶是8°
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富士山8月还会下雪的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般的外头又重又大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推荐穿又轻又暖和的羽绒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽绒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有富士山专柜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富士山 果然很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 这里写了需要的东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}最低限度必须的装备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}头灯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}军用手套
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}登山靴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军用手套
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:52.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要军用手套呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为富士山路上有需要攀登岩石的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军用手套是必需品哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家里好像有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个 头灯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工程中头盔上戴着的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流明？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像代表亮度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流明值越高越亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借你爸爸的不就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把葵拉入山上的可是我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我从父亲那里借也太狡猾了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:38.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面就是羽绒服了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 有好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:49.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:05:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三万九千…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个也是三万
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:05.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个六万？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽绒服真贵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个实在是买不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿几件毛衫 把我的外套也穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能管用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:25.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 正月的时候 妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊葵 我买了流行的羽绒服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟妈妈借羽绒服就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也跟爸爸借头灯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是已经决定要买了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:51.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快买 快买
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:06:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有羽绒服的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽绒服？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:10.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过现在是夏天呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:13.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想在登富士山的时候穿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富士山？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说夏天也很冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.41,0:07:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做日出登山
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要在山顶看日出 登山的时候是深夜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深夜登富士山？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登山本来就很危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还晚上去登？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说了 你是女孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近晚上外出还增多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有好好学习吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期末考试你的名次也下降了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那跟现在没关系吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会让你晚上登山的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.19,0:08:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 葵要登富士山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我担心她遇到危险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她明明对大山没有兴趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:38.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是有了真正喜欢的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得那是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我进来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以聊聊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 登山开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前和朋友去登三增峠了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富士山看起来很漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这次才要去爬富士山吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不止是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也明白妈妈的心情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一的女儿突然说要夜里登山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然会很担心的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:34.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果葵真的想登的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:39.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就得好好说明告诉她「不用担心」 说服她哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不打扰你了 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 我还是想登富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 你还在说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富士山呢 是初学者也能登的山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是夜里登山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:16.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是趁天还亮的时候去靠近山顶的山中小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:20.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜里登山也只是天亮前的两三个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同一个学校习惯登山的前辈也跟我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行动预定也提前全都教给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手机也会保持畅通 我会经常联系的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 求你了 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来她是绝对不会屈服的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:47.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只同意这一次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为交换 刚才的约定一定要遵守哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
